    "title": "HIARCS Chess Explorer",
    "pageid": 3565,
    "redirects": [],
    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> * HIARCS Chess Explorer</b>\n</p><p><b>HIARCS Chess Explorer</b>,<br />\na sophisticated, commercial chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> for <a href=\"/IBM_PC\" title=\"IBM PC\">PC</a> or <a href=\"/Macintosh\" title=\"Macintosh\">Macintosh</a> computers to run under <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> or <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a>, designed and developed by <a href=\"/Michal_Rudolf\" title=\"Michal Rudolf\">Michal Rudolf</a> and <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a>. It is sold in bundle with the <a href=\"/HIARCS\" title=\"HIARCS\">HIARCS 14</a> engine based on the program which won the <a href=\"/WCSC_2011\" title=\"WCSC 2011\">WCSC 2011</a>, and is able to use any <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine. Chess Explorer provides a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tab_%28GUI%29\">tabbed document interface</a>, one document associated with a <a href=\"/Chess_Game\" title=\"Chess Game\">chess game</a> in playing or analyzing mode, either started from the <a href=\"/Initial_Position\" title=\"Initial Position\">initial position</a> or selected from a list of games, the universe or subset from a query result of a <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">PGN</a> <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">database</a>, for re-play with further analysis with new variants and editing annotations. A tabbed window consists of tiled areas with sub- or child windows, the <a href=\"/GUI#BoardWindow\" title=\"GUI\">chess board</a>, <a href=\"/GUI#NotationWindow\" title=\"GUI\">notation</a>, <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> statistics, analysis, and database list or query result windows. The surrounding <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Window_%28computing%29\">frame window</a> uses the classical <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Title_bar\">title-</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Menu_%28computing%29\">menu-</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toolbar\">toolbar</a> at the top of the frame and a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Status_bar\">status bar</a> at the bottom.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Screenshots\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshots</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Windows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Windows</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Mac_OS\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mac OS</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshots\">Screenshots</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshots\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Windows\"><a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Windows\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/pc-chess-explorer.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"HCE-main3.jpg\" src=\"/images/8/86/HCE-main3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"413\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> Chess Explorer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mac_OS\"><a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Mac OS\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/mac-chess-explorer.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Mac-hce-main4.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Mac-hce-main4.png/640px-Mac-hce-main4.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"435\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Mac-hce-main4.png/960px-Mac-hce-main4.png 1.5x, /images/d/d7/Mac-hce-main4.png 2x\" /></a></div> \n<p>Mac Chess Explorer <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=4376\">Chess Explorer</a> by tomgdrums, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Customer Support &amp; Announcements Forum</a>, September 07, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=5020\">HIARCS Chess Explorer is released!</a> by <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Customer Support &amp; Announcements Forum</a>, August 26, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=5063\">HIARCS Chess Explorer tips</a> by <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Customer Support &amp; Announcements Forum</a>, August 29, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44960\">review of the new hiarcs explorer</a> by Joseph, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 31, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=5178\">Hiarcs Chess Explorer for Mac and PC - Quick tour videos</a> by <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Customer Support &amp; Announcements Forum</a>, September 28, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=6117\">Hiarcs Chess Explorer 1.5 released</a> by <a href=\"/Harvey_Williamson\" title=\"Harvey Williamson\">Harvey Williamson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Customer Support &amp; Announcements Forum</a>, July 27, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50908\">If Every Chess company was like this....</a> by <a href=\"/Fernando_Villegas\" title=\"Fernando Villegas\">Fernando Villegas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53600\">Hiarcs Explorer GUI</a> by David Overton, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=79025\">Hiarcs Chess Explorer Pro - Coming Soon! (Now Released)</a> by <a href=\"/Harvey_Williamson\" title=\"Harvey Williamson\">Harvey Williamson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 2022</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/chess-explorer.htm\">HIARCS Chess Explorer - World class chess database and chess playing program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/pc-chess-explorer.htm\">PC Chess Explorer - World class PC chess database and chess playing program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/mac-chess-explorer.htm\">Mac Chess Explorer - World class Mac chess database and chess playing program</a></li>\n<li> HIARCS Chess Explorer for Apple Mac - Quick tour, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/MtBdRjtrBDU?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=HIARCS_Chess_Explorer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/pc-chess-explorer.htm\">PC Chess Explorer - World class PC chess database and chess playing program</a></span>\n</li>